{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Screen.availLeft","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Screen/availLeft","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Screen\"><code>Screen</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Screen/availHeight\"><code>availHeight</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><em><code>availLeft</code></em></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Screen/availTop\"><code>availTop</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Screen/availWidth\"><code>availWidth</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Screen/colorDepth\"><code>colorDepth</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Screen/height\"><code>height</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Screen/left\"><code>left</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Screen/mozBrightness\"><code>mozBrightness</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Screen/mozEnabled\"><code>mozEnabled</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Screen/orientation\"><code>orientation</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Screen/pixelDepth\"><code>pixelDepth</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Screen/orientationchange_event\"><code>Screen: orientationchange event</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Screen/top\"><code>top</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Screen/width\"><code>width</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Screen/lockOrientation\"><code>lockOrientation()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Screen/unlockOrientation\"><code>unlockOrientation()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"概述","title":"概述","isH3":true,"content":"<p>返回浏览器可用空间左边距离屏幕（系统桌面）左边界的距离。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: plain notranslate\">iAvail = window.screen.availLeft\n</pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: plain notranslate\">setY = window.screen.height - window.screen.availTop;\nsetX = window.screen.width - window.screen.availLeft;\nwindow.moveTo(setX, setY);\n</pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"备注","title":"备注","isH3":true,"content":"<p>大多数情况下，该属性返回 0。</p>\n<p>如果你在有两个屏幕的电脑上使用该属性，在右侧屏幕计算该属性值时，返回左侧屏幕的宽度（单位：像素），也即左侧屏幕左边界的 X 坐标。</p>\n<p>在 Windows 中，该属性值取决于哪个屏幕被设为主屏幕，返回相对于主屏幕左边界的 X 坐标。就是说，即使主屏幕不是左侧的屏幕，它的左边界的 X 坐标也是返回 0。如果副屏幕在主屏幕的左侧，则它拥有负的 X 坐标。</p>\n<p>[1] [2] - 左屏幕 <em>availLeft</em> 返回 <strong>0</strong>，右侧的屏幕返回左侧屏幕的宽度</p>\n<p>[2] [1] - 左侧屏幕 <em>availLeft</em> 返回该屏幕的 <strong>-width</strong>，右侧屏幕返回 <strong>0</strong></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":true,"content":"<p>DOM Level 0。不属于任何规范。</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"返回浏览器可用空间左边距离屏幕（系统桌面）左边界的距离。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Screen.availLeft","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Screen.availLeft","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/screen/availleft","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/screen/availleft/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Screen","title":"Screen"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Screen/availLeft","title":